 1994-01681994-01-270,  ,  ,  ,  ,  CAN PORTS,  TC
PrecisAuthority for the VANCOUVER PORT CORPORATION (a) to acquire title from the Crown with respect to 37 acres of land (Maplewood North) situated on the north side of Dollarton Highway in North Vancouver, British Columbia, (b) to sell that land to UNITED PROPERTIES LIMITED, and (c) to amend the lease held by Canadian International College Inc. so as to reduce the proportions of the demised premises.
